Unicron/Teufel/Vehement:




Unicron remained working on Teufel, nearly completed while Vehement 
disengaged from the golden hue tendril of the Guardian computer.

He looked around to Unicron and was a little confused.  He knew about 50% of 
the information he had taken in (and he had taken in quite a bit), but the 
other half was slowly coming to him in bits and pieces.  "Obviously not made 
for Cybertronians." he mused to himself.
